    "body": "The whole jekyll + livereload + jekyll assets field is a complete mess. Not because of our requirements/usage, it's just a mess solved by either doing code (gulp, grunt) or using extensions that are failing like we see right now.\n\nI suggest we move to middleman very soon because I already spent one hour trying to figure out what's not working.\n",
